    public enum MifareSamResults

    Defines all the error codes the MifareSAM APIs returns.

        public static final MifareSamResults AUTH_COND_NOT_SATISFIED

SAM in AV2 mode: Key entry disabled, no Host Key type, startup host authentication accomplished, no lock/unlock key, not key zero, unlock key number and version mismatch, no AES key type, KUC limit exceeded or Unknown key type.
